A4.text: Maria Augusta von Trapp DHS (née Kutschera; 26 January 1905 – 28 March 1987), often styled as 'Baroness', was the stepmother and matriarch of the Trapp Family.

A5.text: The film version set US box office records, and Maria von Trapp received about $500,000 ($5.45 million today) in royalties.
